These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, fuchsia, aquamarine, ivory
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, fantasy, epic, superhero
1. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
2. the person who likes fuchsia is not the person watching spy movies##6
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person who likes white is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person watching spy movies is not the person who likes aquamarine##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | fuchsia   | ivory    | white    | aquamarine |
| Sport      | superhero | spy | epic | fantasy |

