.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
House: gothic-revival, tower, cottage, ranch-style
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, house, folk, electronic
1. the fan salsa is on the far right##1
2. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
3. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
4. the tower house is not the fan house##6
5. the fan electronic is on the left of the cottage house##1
6. the fan salsa is on the right of the fan folk##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
8. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | tower  | cottage    | gothic-revival | ranch-style    |
| Food       | electronic | house | folk  | salsa |

