.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
4 different games are played: whist, bridge, snooker, backgammon
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, indian, british, nigerian
1. the person playing backgammon is not the turkish##6
2. the indian is not the person playing snooker##6
3. the british is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
4. the indian is the person playing whist##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the indian##1
6. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
7. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
8. the british is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | backgammon       | bridge  | whist  | snooker |
| Job        | british | nigerian | indian | turkish  |

