.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, engineer, firefighter, librarian
House: cottage, craftsman, townhouse, cape-cod
1. the firefighter is on the left of the librarian##1
2. the engineer is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
3. the cape-cod house is not the engineer##6
4. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
6. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | engineer | firefighter | librarian     | architect |
| Transport   | craftsman     | townhouse    | cottage | cape-cod    |

