.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, whist, mah-jongg, canasta
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, russian, malaysian, german
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
3. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
4. the person playing whist is not the german##6
5. the australian is not the person playing scrabble##6
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing whist##1
7. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | scrabble        | canasta | mah-jongg | whist |
| Transport   | german | australian | russian     | malaysian   |

