.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, coffee, tea, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, strawberry, artichoke, banana
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the person eating strawberry##6
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
4. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
5. the person drinking tea is the person drinking tea##1
6. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
8. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
9. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | coffee | tea    | water  | lemonade   |
| Nationality   | artichoke  | banana | strawberry | pomegranate |

