.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, volleyball, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, car, helicopter, airplane
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
2. the person driving the helicopter is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
3. the person who's sport is surfing is the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is the person driving the subway##1
7. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | handball | cricket     | volleyball | surfing |
| Music-Genre   | helicopter | subway | airplane      | car         |

