2. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
5. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
7. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
8. the person playing domino is not the person watching spy movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | domino  | whist        | canasta      | snooker          |
| Job        | time-travel | western | spy | zombie |

