.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
City: hamburg, miami, san-francisco, london
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, paramedic, dressmaker, chef
1. the police-officer is not the person traveling to hamburg##6
2. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the chef is the chef##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the right of the chef##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is not the chef##6
6. the paramedic is not the person traveling to miami##6
7. the chef is in an even position##4
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | san-francisco | hamburg        | london  | miami     |
| Sport   | police-officer     | chef | paramedic | dressmaker |

