.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, superhero, animation, western
4 different pets are kept: fish, turtle, pony, mouse
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
3. the owner of the pony is not the person watching animation movies##6
4. the person watching superhero movies is between the owner of the mouse and the person watching animation movies##2
5. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
6. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the fish and the person watching drama movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | animation | superhero    | drama | western |
| Music-Genre   | fish         | turtle | mouse   | pony     |

