4. the french is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
8. the french is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | skateboarding | ice-hockey | tennis | rowing |
| Pet     | australian  | argentine      | german  | french       |

